faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為舊式棍波頭係圓姑碌，似個波，所以叫波棍<br />\n之後所有同佢相關嘅都叫咗波。（好似係）"},{"pid":"ca85c297aec96ee284360cbc5ba91a370f394bba","tid":6324,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>棍波<br />\n自動波<br />\n波箱<br />\n<br />\ngearbox同個波字有咩關係?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n波段 咁裝住佢既就叫波箱 唔鐘意既你可以自己直譯波盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係想知同個波字有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為舊式棍波頭係圓姑碌，似個波，所以叫波棍<br />\n之後所有同佢相關嘅都叫咗波。（好似係）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmake sense"}]}